---
title: Easy Pulled Chicken & Potato Salad with Garlic Yoghurt, Almonds & Parmesan
description: Feeling like something fresh and tasty, low-carb and easy? May we present our Greek-style pulled chicken seasoned in garlic. Tender and simply yum, resting on top of a crisp salad, sprinkled with cheese and garnished with almonds, this dish is perfect to ring in these warmer spring days (or any day for that matter)!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
